      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GLISTENING (8) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (24.34) in a Mix 3/4 at Bendigo latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. PATRIOT CILLA (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.37) at Warrnambool behind Lightning Range in a Free For All. Has the pace to be prominent. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Hard to beat again. WHODAT JEWEL (5) was out of the placings last time when fifth at Warrnambool (25.92) but scored four back at Geelong (26.00). Can do much better this time. NOT SORRY (1) is a last start winner who can measure up again.",
